    <article class="copy reveal-up">
      <div class="kicker">Peacock · Shimmer & Becoming</div>
      <h2>Bejeweled: Shimmer & Becoming</h2>
      <p>And then there’s Bejeweled. My peacock. My queen. My declaration. For years, I wore the mask of “everything is perfect” while I broke inside. Bejeweled is me, unmasked. She is feathers spread wide, shimmer unapologetic. She’s the reminder that the little girl inside me has finally arrived — radiant, worthy, seen.</p>
      <div class="caption">
        <p><em>Bejeweled the peacock amigurumi.</em></p>
        <p><em>Bejeweled — the moment of becoming, stitched in unapologetic shimmer.</em></p>
      </div>
    </article>
